messages.message:
this is occurring for me on both prod (gif 1) and uat (gif 2) if there's no doc assigned to that queue

note in the gif that the issue occurs for "escalation queue" but not for "review queue"

Note that I just filed this - seeing a similar 'Error occurred executing GRPC method' while trying to edit field values in human review. I marked it as a blocker due to lack of workaround and potential customer impact: https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-4574

The same issue doesn't occur on aihub-sandbox.
